{"tid":1561663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家可唔可以專注番我地要既五大訴求？","createTime":"2019-09-11T16:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T14:29:24.000Z","uid":41873,"like":76,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9a7fdfc31cf11c5a21e3e9858506164e26316bf7","tid":1561663,"uid":41873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我明白［願榮耀歸香港］係首好能夠代表到真香港人既歌，呢個不能認同更多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但9月15亦都係我地出黎繼續爭取我地<span style=\"color: gold;\">初心</span>既時候！！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位手足叫呢句口號叫左咁耐，唔好因為國旗國歌首都呢類野而令大家偏離左<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更重要既目的</span></span></strong>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>黑警繼續擴大權力周街打人，<br />\n醫護界比黑警濫權控制，<br />\n大量手足被捕，被姦，被打到頭破血流，比狗打完唔敢去醫院，<br />\n柒婆完全無視香港人訴求走去探閘機，<br />\n中共出一堆垃圾文宣話我地暴徒搞港獨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係想掃大家興，我係度只係想提醒所有手足要記住我地個初心！</span><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！齊上齊落！</span></span></strong> 唔好比位人入！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>915民陣大遊行願所有香港人一齊唱香港之歌爭取我地一直堅持既野<br />\n3pm cwb東角道見！！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3a8505904c9168c8ab88b8b671ea83eeabe08492","tid":1561663,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><s